title: Electricity prices for households in Denmark 2010 - 2019 , semi-annually
summary: Overall Euro cents per kilowatt-hour has increased over the Year.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year 2013_S2 and 2014_S1.
Maximum Euro cents per kilowatt-hour, about 30.88 was reported at Year 2016_S1
Minimum Euro cents per kilowatt-hour about 29.08 was reached at Year 2011_S1
min_summary: Overall Euro cents per kilowatt-hour has increased over the Year.
mid_summary: In general Euro cents per kilowatt-hour has stayed the same over the Year.
The most drastic increase took place within the Year 2013_S2 and 2014_S1.
Maximum Euro cents per kilowatt-hour, about 30.88 was reported at Year 2016_S1
Minimum Euro cents per kilowatt-hour about 29.08 was reached at Year 2011_S1
